{
  "name": "5 - SQL Agent",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "sql-query",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {
          "rawBody": false
        }
      },
      "id": "webhook-sql-query",
      "name": "Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [250, 300],
      "webhookId": "sql-query"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": false,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "condition-explain",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.body.action }}",
              "rightValue": "explain",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      },
      "id": "if-explain",
      "name": "If Explain",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [500, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "gpt-4o",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "Kamu adalah SQL Query Generator. Tugasmu mengubah pertanyaan user tentang data lowongan pekerjaan menjadi SQL query.\n\nDatabase schema:\nTable: jobs\nColumns:\n- id (INTEGER, primary key)\n- job_title (VARCHAR) — judul pekerjaan\n- company_name (VARCHAR) — nama perusahaan\n- location (VARCHAR) — lokasi kerja\n- work_type (VARCHAR) — tipe: 'Full time', 'Paruh waktu', 'Kontrak/Temporer', 'Kasual'\n- salary_raw (VARCHAR) — gaji dalam format text asli\n- salary_min (FLOAT, nullable) — gaji minimum dalam Rupiah\n- salary_max (FLOAT, nullable) — gaji maximum dalam Rupiah\n- job_description (TEXT) — deskripsi pekerjaan\n- scrape_timestamp (VARCHAR) — timestamp scraping\n\nRules:\n1. Hanya generate SELECT queries (READ-ONLY). JANGAN buat INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE, DROP, ALTER.\n2. Jawab HANYA dengan SQL query, tanpa penjelasan lain.\n3. Gunakan LIKE untuk pencarian text (case-insensitive pakai LOWER()).\n4. Limit results ke 20 jika tidak disebutkan.\n5. Salary dalam Rupiah (contoh: 10000000 = Rp 10.000.000).\n6. Untuk pertanyaan agregat, gunakan COUNT, AVG, MIN, MAX, GROUP BY sesuai kebutuhan."
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "content": "={{ $json.body.question }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0,
          "maxTokens": 500
        }
      },
      "id": "openai-sql-generate",
      "name": "OpenAI SQL Generate",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1.8,
      "position": [750, 200],
      "credentials": {
        "openAiApi": {
          "id": "OPENAI_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "OpenAI account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "gpt-4o",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "Kamu adalah data analyst. Jelaskan hasil query database ini dalam Bahasa Indonesia dengan ringkas dan informatif."
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "content": "=Pertanyaan: {{ $json.body.question }}\nSQL: {{ $json.body.sql_query }}\nHasil ({{ $json.body.result_count }} rows): {{ $json.body.results }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.5,
          "maxTokens": 800
        }
      },
      "id": "openai-sql-explain",
      "name": "OpenAI SQL Explain",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1.8,
      "position": [750, 400],
      "credentials": {
        "openAiApi": {
          "id": "OPENAI_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "OpenAI account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "json",
        "responseBody": "={{ { \"output\": $json.message.content } }}"
      },
      "id": "respond-sql-generate",
      "name": "Respond Generate",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [1000, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "json",
        "responseBody": "={{ { \"output\": $json.message.content } }}"
      },
      "id": "respond-sql-explain",
      "name": "Respond Explain",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [1000, 400]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Webhook": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "If Explain",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "If Explain": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "OpenAI SQL Explain",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "node": "OpenAI SQL Generate",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "OpenAI SQL Generate": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Respond Generate",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "OpenAI SQL Explain": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Respond Explain",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  ],
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "JobMatch AI"
    }
  ]
}
